		<div class="courseListDescription">Creative industries have tremendous potential to foster social inclusion and societal betterment through creativity and innovation. This intensive on-site exploration of an international creative center like Berlin or Buenos Aires exposes students to best practices of social innovation. Using design thinking methodology, students then leverage the creative industries' power to propose solutions to pressing social issues. For senior students, this Spring/Summer course is not offered every year. Students bear costs for transportation, room and board.</div>
	
	
