		<div class="courseListDescription">This directed reading course is intended to permit the student to survey a coherent body of literature in an area of study related to the student's program objectives.</div>
	
	
		<div class="courseListLength"><span class="courseInfoLabels">Weekly Contact: </span><span class="courseInfoValues">Tutorial: 1 hr. </span></div>
	
	
